Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:25.72,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}In these flames of war
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:31.94,CQEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}We're rising up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:40.39,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}阴影挟着危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:45.10,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}茫茫荒野 得失不断上演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:50.94,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}但在可怖的黑暗中间 只要愿意放眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:54.95,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}光明依然可见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.20,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:03.12,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}一线希望就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:09.54,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}共同燃起 革命的狼烟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.17,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}来 别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:19.93,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}哪怕被命运视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.31,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}渺小的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:28.48,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}也要坚持向前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.99,CQCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}光明必将出现
